body:
> @John-44 just to be 100% sure, we do not want normal members to have access to others' revealed accounts right?

@jrainville if you are referring to wallet accounts (I assume you are) then members **definitely** shouldn’t just be able to see (or be able to find out in any way) the wallet addresses of other members.

Only mechanism by which users can choose to share their addresses with other users is use the Profile Shocase and opt-in (which is nothing to do with communities)
